about.summary: Python wrapper for the PubChem PUG REST API.

name: pubchempy
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "PubChemPy" %}
{% set version = "1.0.4" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 24e9dc2fc90ab153b2764bf805e510b1410700884faf0510a9e7cf0d61d8ed0e

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python
    - pandas >=0.16.2

test:
  imports:
    - pubchempy

about:
  home: https://github.com/mcs07/PubChemPy
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'Python wrapper for the PubChem PUG REST API.'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - hadim
